text: César Solari (born 2 November 1946) is an Ecuadorian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 52 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:Ecuadorian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Ecuador Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Guayaquil
